---
title: Heap Sort  |  O(n log n) · Space O(n)
---
flowchart TD
    classDef startEnd fill:#22c55e,stroke:#15803d,color:#fff
    classDef decision fill:#f59e0b,stroke:#b45309,color:#fff
    classDef process fill:#3b82f6,stroke:#1d4ed8,color:#fff
    classDef result fill:#8b5cf6,stroke:#6d28d9,color:#fff

    A([Start]):::startEnd --> B["Add all elements to a min-heap PriorityQueue"]:::process
    B --> C{"Heap empty?"}:::decision
    C -- No --> D["poll() · removes smallest element"]:::process
    D --> E["Write to next position in sorted array"]:::process
    E --> C
    C -- Yes --> F([Array is sorted]):::result
